Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.00,0:01:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天草翔伍与圣母小姐的秘密？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.93,0:01:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.67,0:02:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个秘密就隐藏在\N岛原发生的悲剧之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.34,0:02:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第七十二话\N追忆的日子  翔伍与小夜的悲伤过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.78,0:02:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是翔伍大人 翔伍大人呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.16,0:02:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一年前\N天草翔伍来到岛原以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.93,0:02:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻统率所有天主教徒\N培育士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.03,0:02:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时也设立了孤儿院与医院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.61,0:02:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.44,0:02:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是翔伍大人\N亲自开的处方药哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.12,0:02:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦一下子就减退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.59,0:02:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简直不像真的\N身体变得轻松多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.53,0:03:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只要早晚喝下这个药\N不久以后身体就会复原了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.10,0:03:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢您了 太感谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.24,0:03:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是奇迹呀\N翔伍大人又创造奇迹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.97,0:03:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他治好绝症病人了\N果然是天草四郎的转世呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.68,0:03:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是神子呀\N翔伍大人要为我们创造神国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.15,0:03:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于\N可以脱离悲惨生活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.42,0:03:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三百年来我们一直躲躲藏藏\N以后再也不必躲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.43,0:03:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望的国度要来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.47,0:03:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家听好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.00,0:03:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天是圣灵的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.97,0:03:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要悼念14年前\N为村子殉教的人们的灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.81,0:03:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣灵的日子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.28,0:03:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是翔伍大人的父母亲\N蒙主宠召的日子哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.95,0:03:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要在灵庙里面闭关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.05,0:03:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也可以去吗\N请让我们一起祈祷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.86,0:04:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要祈祷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.86,0:04:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我们一起献上祈祷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.30,0:04:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天草翔伍为何可以治疗病人\N预言天灾地变呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是奇迹也不是魔术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.37,0:04:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是由于他在大陆城市\N学会西方医学与天文学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.54,0:04:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本身知识渊博
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.88,0:04:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.25,0:04:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轻松就得到\N万能救世主之名的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.39,0:04:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却有一个治不了的病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.46,0:04:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,治不了的病？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.26,0:04:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他妹妹圣母小姐生病了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.87,0:04:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且跟\N夺走他母亲生命的病一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.04,0:04:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不治之症
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.82,0:05:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能够动吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.68,0:05:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.05,0:05:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我作梦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.42,0:05:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纯白的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.82,0:05:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天那一天又来临了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.39,0:05:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸妈妈蒙主宠召的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.73,0:05:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.53,0:05:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岛原在梦境里面是白色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.37,0:05:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都闪闪发亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.98,0:06:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家人在一起的最后一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.85,0:06:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天…又要来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.03,0:06:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快来呀 小夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.30,0:06:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.67,0:06:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈 你不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.38,0:06:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翔伍 小夜 别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.11,0:06:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你们先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.92,0:06:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.02,0:06:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 请保佑我的家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.60,0:06:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保佑我的家人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.67,0:07:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.48,0:07:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸现在跟你讲的事\N你终生都不可以忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.41,0:07:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.68,0:07:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大约250年来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.28,0:07:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岛原居民一直瞒着幕府\N保有自己的信仰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.76,0:07:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是隐藏的天主教徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.56,0:07:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为心怀信仰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.86,0:07:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家才能够\N忍受苛刻的劳动工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.67,0:07:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我尽己所能保护人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是神的教诲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.31,0:07:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人的灵魂都是平等的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.11,0:07:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人的灵魂都是平等的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.72,0:07:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神说：
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.42,0:07:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人活着的价值\N不在于身份与财富
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.76,0:07:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在于那心灵的高贵与美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.36,0:08:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我终生都不会抛弃这个教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.96,0:08:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我大概\N很快就会被逮捕判刑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.57,0:08:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.67,0:08:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好了\N你跟小夜就逃去大陆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.18,0:08:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今夜你叔叔兵卫会来接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.75,0:08:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就跟兵卫走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.75,0:08:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸跟妈妈呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.82,0:08:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.26,0:08:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要变强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.99,0:08:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天\N你会成为岛原人民的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸把一切都托付给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.03,0:08:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必需变强 像神一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.74,0:08:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像神一样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.17,0:08:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算在遥远的异国流浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.14,0:08:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是要想办法回来岛原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.78,0:08:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后保护大家\N这些被虐待的人民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.36,0:09:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是武藤时贞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.56,0:09:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.03,0:09:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个天主教的混蛋\N相信异国神的叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.34,0:09:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.34,0:09:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.71,0:09:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翔伍…将来…一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.95,0:09:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要成为岛原人民的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.84,0:09:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 振作点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.74,0:09:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.41,0:09:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翔伍 小夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.51,0:09:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.81,0:09:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些人真笨 信什么神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.12,0:10:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抛弃信仰就可以活命了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.79,0:10:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然因此忍受酷刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.15,0:10:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为神抛弃自己的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.76,0:10:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要抛弃就抛弃啊\N反正他们的生命连条虫都不值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.50,0:10:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对呀 他们就照他们的教义\N快乐的上天国吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.07,0:10:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有活着的 这女人命真大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.04,0:10:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们看要怎么办？\N正好可以散心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.41,0:10:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手 不准对妈妈下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.45,0:10:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.11,0:10:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准碰她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.52,0:10:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这小子好像也不要命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.39,0:10:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.39,0:10:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.66,0:10:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我来接你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.17,0:10:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兵卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.44,0:10:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.24,0:11:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 船在那边等着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.25,0:11:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.15,0:11:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去只会拖累你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.42,0:11:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就带着这两个孩子逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.42,0:11:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.49,0:11:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.79,0:11:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 翔伍 小夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.32,0:11:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 妈妈也要跟大家一起走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.69,0:11:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翔伍 你不听妈的话了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.70,0:11:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是留下妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.17,0:11:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胆小鬼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.84,0:11:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是将来要领导许多人的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要抛弃小小的怜悯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必需变强 像钢铁一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.58,0:11:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你死在这里的话\N岛原人民的希望就毁灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.38,0:11:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要逃 翔伍\N而且要活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.19,0:11:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.19,0:11:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.49,0:11:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.33,0:11:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.59,0:11:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小夜 这个你拿着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.70,0:11:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兵卫 拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.17,0:11:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.44,0:12:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.27,0:12:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好 翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.24,0:12:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好保护小夜\N保护小夜啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.64,0:13:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翔伍 你要变强 像神一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.68,0:13:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是将来要领导许多人的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.62,0:13:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要抛弃小小的怜悯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.06,0:13:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天你一定要回来岛原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.72,0:13:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后保护大家\N这些被虐待的人民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要变强 我一定要变强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不屈服于任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.87,0:13:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都不能践踏我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.47,0:13:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要成为神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为神 回来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.51,0:13:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保护这里被欺凌的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.06,0:14:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.40,0:14:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就可以去天国了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.70,0:14:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去爸爸妈妈的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.34,0:14:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是神的祝福呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都别说了 别说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.55,0:14:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你死的\N我一定要守住你的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.13,0:14:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村你怎么有办法这么快\N一点也不像失明的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是跟随小操的足音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.91,0:14:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,足音？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.91,0:14:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且从大家的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.78,0:15:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隐约也可以\N感觉到周围有什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.48,0:15:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说…\N我们都成了你的眼睛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是剑心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.36,0:15:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉 果然不是常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.74,0:15:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有船…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.38,0:15:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的 在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.59,0:15:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是山东 荷兰领事馆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.99,0:15:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨夜我也有看到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.56,0:15:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山东
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.19,0:15:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他会在这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.83,0:15:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可能是被利用了 应该
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.20,0:15:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被这个王国的干部之一\N傀王所利用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.64,0:15:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傀王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.04,0:15:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 大有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.41,0:15:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按照我收集到的情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.04,0:16:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傀王这个人其实在德川时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.28,0:16:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就被我们御庭番众列为\N最重要危险人物而盯梢着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.62,0:16:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,御庭番众也…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传教师傀王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.49,0:16:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他母亲是隐藏的天主教徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.36,0:16:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时受到幕府镇压\N渡海到大陆去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.69,0:16:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在大陆生下傀王过世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.50,0:16:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傀王不知生父是谁\N一个人在地狱挣扎生存下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.07,0:16:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他诅咒夺走自己国籍的\N日本这个国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.57,0:16:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,满怀怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.41,0:16:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁着幕末的混乱时期\N偷偷在九州登陆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.75,0:16:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从此就虎视眈眈\N等待向这个国家报仇的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.36,0:16:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傀王的本质\N似乎跟天草翔伍相差很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.94,0:17:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是信号 他在送信号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.08,0:17:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不会是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.31,0:17:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,军队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.32,0:17:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.48,0:17:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 只有可能是军队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.32,0:17:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.97,0:17:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣母小姐 您在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.37,0:17:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,源右卫门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您果然在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.81,0:17:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣母小姐 我想报告您一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.55,0:17:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚…到底有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.65,0:17:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.69,0:17:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那绝对是您的项链\N不会错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.69,0:17:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的项链？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.43,0:18:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在傀王大人那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的没骗我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.50,0:18:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我说几次才懂\N你这个石头脑袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.70,0:18:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的天使的项链\N被金发的男人拿走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.98,0:18:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你说的话是真的\N项链可能在傀王大人那里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.88,0:18:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才问你\N走哪条路才可以找到傀王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.52,0:18:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你问事情不够礼貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.32,0:18:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 你别过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.02,0:18:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.49,0:18:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.90,0:18:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.60,0:18:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那地方有什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.03,0:18:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你们的王国耶\N你不知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.94,0:18:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是去年才从大陆过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.31,0:18:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这地方是\N傀王大人几年前就建立的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傀王拿走我的项链…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.02,0:20:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.52,0:20:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天草翔伍 这是他的濒死之图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.42,0:20:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明早这张图会成为现实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.01,0:20:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傀王 你想背叛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.75,0:20:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背叛？我打一开始就在想\N要如何让你们兄妹死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.32,0:20:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明早圣灵的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.79,0:20:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救世主会如这张图所画的升天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.99,0:20:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是打动民众心灵的\N传说中的死法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.90,0:20:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我成为\N传布他的教导的大司教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.37,0:20:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传布？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.14,0:21:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天草翔伍的预言书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.91,0:21:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面写了很多\N令信徒感激涕零的预言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.08,0:21:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救世主死后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.62,0:21:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信徒们\N应该会发誓绝对服从吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.39,0:21:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥并没有写预言书啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.96,0:21:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是我写的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.93,0:21:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.76,0:21:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留下永远的预言书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.80,0:21:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天草翔伍成为名符其实\N不会毁灭的神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.93,0:21:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时相信会有数万民众\N哭嚎着为他而战吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.90,0:21:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乱民推翻这个国家\N政权落入荷兰的手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.61,0:21:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我成为殖民地之王\N日本彻底灭亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.01,0:21:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我冒渎这个国家\N埋葬它 达成心愿的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.02,0:21:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傀王呀 你太会胡说八道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.82,0:21:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.33,0:21:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣母小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.39,0:21:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庄三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.76,0:21:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 圣母小姐\N我不会让这种人得逞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.37,0:22:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你这样的怪物\N末路是通往哪里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.14,0:22:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就亲自来\N把你打进地狱的血池里！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.75,0:22:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.32,0:22:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个景观好看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.65,0:22:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.55,0:22:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是恶魔 神决不会原谅你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.89,0:22:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥不会被你杀死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.66,0:22:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣母小姐\N下次在天国见面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.80,0:22:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傀王
